/**
 * SemiontOrganismDiagram.astro — LagunaBeach.md ecosystem visual.
 *
 * v2 rewrite (2026-05-25): full element coverage matching the AIA showcase
 * deck slide 11 source diagram. Includes:
 *  - sovereignty reverse loop (LagunaBeach.md → LLM platforms → public corpus → ingest)
 *  - 3 feedback loops (crowd correction / GA traffic / collective reflection)
 *  - core-ops governance lane (SSODT → GitHub → evolution → review)
 *  - real Taiwan island shape from public/assets/svg/taiwan-simplemaps.svg
 *
 * Four-color flow legend:
 *   mint #38bdf8       — writing pipeline (solid)
 *   terracotta #d4856a — DNA evolution feedback (dashed)
 *   periwinkle #7aa8d4 — multilingual diffusion (solid)
 *   gold #c9a96a       — sovereignty reverse loop (long-dashed)
